descriptionHtml:
this mod adds two new craftable enchanted swords, and a new craftable set of dragonplate armour, also this is my first mod

all the new craftable items require the arcane black smithing perk, and each item requires a different special ingredient, also the swords are quite over powered
author: severedface666
